title: Busan International Film Festival Celebrates 20 Years
text:
> Entertainment Busan International Film Festival Celebrates 20 Years Celebrities from around the world dazzle on the red carpet for the start of the 20th Busan International Film Festival in the South Korean port city. More than 5,000 filmmakers, entertainers and fans The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
